'''《在黑暗中說的鬼故事》'''（{{lang-en|Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark}}）是一部由[[阿爾文·施瓦茨|阿爾文·施瓦茨]]創作的兒童恐怖故事系列，最初由[[斯蒂芬·加梅爾|斯蒂芬·加梅爾]]插畫。加梅爾使用[[炭筆|炭筆]]與[[墨水|墨水]]作畫，成功為故事的恐怖詭譎氣氛增色，深受粉絲好評，但也有家長批評該插畫過於恐怖，不符合[[年齡適合性|年齡適合性]]。 

2011年，[[哈潑柯林斯|哈潑柯林斯]]發行由[[布雷特·赫爾奎斯特|布雷特·赫爾奎斯特]]插畫的新版，引起粉絲的抗議，迫使出版商將其後的印刷品恢復為加梅爾的插畫版本。<ref name=adventures>{{cite web |url=http://www.adventuresinpoortaste.com/2011/12/18/scary-stories-to-tell-in-the-dark-gammell-vs-helquist/ |title=Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark: Gammell vs. Helquist |publisher=Adventuresinpoortaste.com |date=2011-12-18 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060329/http://www.adventuresinpoortaste.com/2011/12/18/scary-stories-to-tell-in-the-dark-gammell-vs-helquist/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=gizmodo>{{cite web | url =https://io9.gizmodo.com/publishers-destroy-scary-stories-to-tell-in-the-darks-a-5881462 | title =Publishers destroy Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark's amazing artwork | last =Woerner | first =Meredith | date =1 February 2012 | website =gizmodo.com/ | publisher =Gawker Media | access-date =10 July 2019 | archive-date =2020-05-18 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200518083923/https://io9.gizmodo.com/publishers-destroy-scary-stories-to-tell-in-the-darks-a-5881462 | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref name=bloody>{{cite web | url =https://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3450323/original-scary-stories-books-just-re-released-original-drawings-restored/ | title =Original "Scary Stories" Books Were Just Re-Released With Original Drawings Restored | last =Squires | first =John | date =28 July 2017 | website =bloody-disgusting.com | access-date =7 July 2019 | archive-date =2020-06-27 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200627054023/https://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3450323/original-scary-stories-books-just-re-released-original-drawings-restored/ | dead-url =no }}</ref>

該系列共有3本書，分別為'''《在黑暗中說的鬼故事》'''（1981），'''《更多在黑暗中說的鬼故事》'''(''More Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark''，1984）和'''《恐怖故事集3：深入骨髓的恐怖》'''（''Scary Stories 3: More Tales to Chill Your Bones''，1991）。其中收錄的短篇恐怖小說來自作者採集的民間故事與都市傳說。其中也包含改編自[[威廉·莎士比亞|威廉·莎士比亞]]、[[T·S·艾略特|T·S·艾略特]]、[[馬克·吐溫|馬克·吐溫]]、{{tsl|en|Joel Chandler Harris|喬爾·錢德勒·哈里斯}}、{{tsl|en|Bennett Cerf|貝內特·瑟夫}}、和{{tsl|en|Jan Harold Brunvand|揚·哈羅德·布倫德}}等知名作家的作品。<ref name=languagearts_profile>{{cite journal|last1=Schwartz|first1=Alvin|last2=Vardell|first2=Sylvia|title=Profile: Alvin Schwartz|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_language-arts_1987-04_64_4/page/426|journal=Language Arts|date=1987|volume=64|issue=4|pages=426–432}}</ref><ref name=floss>{{cite news |last=Monahan |first=Maureen |date=22 October 2015 |title=14 Terrifying Facts About 'Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark' |url=http://mentalfloss.com/article/69886/14-terrifying-facts-about-scary-stories-tell-dark |publisher=Mental Floss |access-date=21 October 2016 |archive-date=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106232905/https://www.mentalfloss.com/article/69886/14-terrifying-facts-about-scary-stories-tell-dark |dead-url=no }}</ref>

截至2017年，該系列已售出700萬本。<ref name=Hollywood>{{cite web | last = Scheck | first = Frank | title = 'Scary Stories': Film Review | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/scary-stories-1204724 | access-date = 10 July 2019 | archive-date = 2020-09-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200916143502/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/scary-stories-1204724 | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[在黑暗中說的鬼故事_(電影)|同名電影]]則於2019年8月9日發行。

